description.plain:
“​don’t wanna break up again” is a song by ​Ariana Grande, released in 2024 as part of her album “eternal sunshine”. The song is a ballad in which Ariana expresses to her lover the pain they are causing to each other. Nonetheless, she has a desire to stay with her lover despite the challenges they face.

The song features Ariana Grande’s signature vocal range and emotional delivery, as well as a chorus of backing vocals. The song is a reflection of Ariana Grande’s personal experience with love and loss, and a testament to her resilience and optimism.
